flowchart LR
    A[Small valid observation] --> B[Classify response]
    B --> C{Response supports expansion?}
    C -- no --> D[Keep scope small or switch probe]
    C -- yes --> E[Choose expansion factor r_i]
    E --> F[Next scope s_{i+1} = r_i s_i]
    F --> G{Adverse boundary risk acceptable?}
    G -- yes --> H[Expand and observe next response]
    G -- no --> I[Reduce r_i or observe sooner]
    H --> B
    I --> B
